      "level": "B1",
      "function": "Make 'if' sentences",
      "source": "contributor",
      "reviewed": true,
      "display_order": 4,
      "explanation": "Idan (or short in) opens real conditions: Idan ka zo, za mu ci abinci (If you come, we will eat), In ta gani, za ta gaya mana (If she sees, she'll tell us). Unreal 'if only' uses dā …: Dā na sani (Had I known).",
